{{main|古代美洲人祭}}
[[玛雅人|玛雅人]]、[[印加人|印加人]]、[[托尔特克人|托尔特克人]]、[[萨波特克人|萨波特克人]]也都有人祭习俗。[[阿兹特克人|阿兹特克人]]的人祭间接地继承自玛雅，但是其规模远比玛雅盛大，例如，1486年，特诺奇蒂特兰大金字塔落成时，阿兹特克统治者一次就下令把两万多名俘虏抬到祭坛上，挖出心脏祭祀太阳神，接着把心脏丢入一尊石头神像所持容器中，再把尸体抛下寺庙的台阶。在[[印加帝国|印加帝国]]建立之前，南美洲地区的[[莫切文化|莫切文化]]、[[纳斯卡文化|纳斯卡文化]]也盛行人牲祭祀，人祭被视为权力的来源，据考古调查纳斯卡文化后期大约有十分之一的人口被献祭。<ref>"The Body Context: Interpreting Early Nasca Decapitation Burials" DeLeonardis, Lisa. ''Latin American Antiquity''. 2000. Vol. 11, No. 4, pp. 363–368.</ref><ref>"A Cache of 48 Nasca Trophy Heads From Cerro Carapo, Peru" by David Browne, Helaine Silverman, and Ruben Garcia, ''Latin American Antiquity'' (1993), Volume 4,  No. 3: 274–294</ref><ref>{{Citation |last=Proulx |first=Donald A. |title=Paracas and Nasca: Regional Cultures on the South Coast of Peru |date=2008 |url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/978-0-387-74907-5_29 |work=The Handbook of South American Archaeology |pages=563–585 |editor-last=Silverman |editor-first=Helaine |place=New York, NY |publisher=Springer New York |language=en |doi=10.1007/978-0-387-74907-5_29 |isbn=978-0-387-74906-8 |access-date=2022-02-07 |editor2-last=Isbell |editor2-first=William H.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Vaughn |first=Kevin J. |date=2008-06-28 |title=Crafts and the Materialization of Chiefly Power in Nasca |url=https://anthrosource.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/pdfdirect/10.1525/ap3a.2004.14.113 |journal=Archeological Papers of the American Anthropological Association |volume=14 |issue=1 |pages=113–130 |doi=10.1525/ap3a.2004.14.113 |issn=1551-823X}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |last=Marie. |first=Kellner, Corina |url=http://worldcat.org/oclc/52536451 |title=Coping with environmental and social challenges in prehistoric Peru : bioarchaeological analyses of Nasca populations |oclc=52536451}}</ref>

=== 撒哈拉以南非洲 ===
在西非，人祭在19世紀前仍十分普遍，國王或王后去世后，奴隸，囚犯和俘虜經常會被獻祭。最有名的是[[约鲁巴人|约鲁巴人]]的人祭和[[達荷美王國|達荷美王國]]的年度祭，年度祭中成百上千的囚犯將被殺害(也影響了[[海地|海地]]的[[巫毒教|巫毒教]]活人獻祭)。

